T1  - Simulating Housing Market Processes at the Micro Level
AU  - Ayal, Igal
AU  - Hempel, Donald J.
Y1  - 1979/06/01
PY  - 1979
DA  - 1979/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.25.6.565
