T2  - Management Science
JF  - Management Science
JO  - Management Science
SP  - 565
EP  - 576
VL  - 25
IS  - 6
PB  - INFORMS
N2  - The article describes a simulation of market processes in single-family, owner-occupied housing in a metropolitan market area. The simulation was designed both as a training tool and a decision aid. Model structure is discussed in detail, and data bases for construction are described. The model has substantial face validity (tested with a sizeable number of prominent Realtors), and interesting managerial implications.
AB  - The article describes a simulation of market processes in single-family, owner-occupied housing in a metropolitan market area. The simulation was designed both as a training tool and a decision aid. Model structure is discussed in detail, and data bases for construction are described. The model has substantial face validity (tested with a sizeable number of prominent Realtors), and interesting managerial implications.
